This test will check that Window Manager Tweaks opens and close correctly
<dl>
    <dt>Open Window Manager Tweaks from Settings menu</dt>
        <dd>Dialogue opens</dd>
    <dt>Press Close</dt>
        <dd>Dialogue closes</dd>
</dl>

This test will check options in Cycling tab
<dl>
    <dt>Open Window Manager Tweaks from Settings menu</dt>
    <dt>Open any application and minimise it</dt>
    <dt>Change to another workspace, open another application</dt>
    <dt>Change back to previous workspace</dt>
    <dt>Press Alt+Tab repeatedly</dt>
        <dd>Applications available are cycled through</dd>
    <dt>Focus on Window Manager Tweaks and select Cycle through windows on all workspaces</dt>
        <dd>Tick appears in box</dd>
    <dt>Press Alt+Tab repeatedly</dt>
        <dd>Applications on all workspaces are cycled through</dd>
    <dt>Deselect Include Hidden windows</dt>
        <dd>Tick removed from box</dd>
    <dt>Press Alt+Tab repeatedly</dt>
        <dd>Applications on all workspaces are cycled through with exception of minimised application</dd>
    <dt>Deselect Draw Frame</dt>
        <dd>Tick removed from box</dd>
    <dt>Press Alt+Tab repeatedly</dt>
        <dd>Applications on all workspaces are cycled through without frame around selected window</dd>
</dl>

This test will check some options in Compositor tab
<dl>
    <dt>Open Window Manager Tweaks from Settings menu, select Compositor tab</dt>
        <dd>Dialogue changes to compositor tab</dd>
    <dt>Change value of opacity of windows during move to approximately 50%</dt>
        <dd>Slider position changes and stays where moved to</dd>
    <dt>Grab Window Tweak setting window by title bar and move window</dt>
        <dd>While window moves - window is slightly transparent</dd>
    <dt>Deselect Enable window compositing</dt>
        <dd>Tick removed from box</dd>
    <dt>Grab Window Tweak setting window by title bar and move window</dt>
        <dd>While window moves - window is completely opaque</dd>
    <dt>Enable display compositing and deselect Show shadows under regular windows</dt>
        <dd>Shadows disappear from window</dd>
</dl>

<strong>If all actions produce the expected results listed, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'passed' result.
    If an action fails, or produces an unexpected result, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> 'failed' and <a href="../../buginstructions">file a bug</a>. Please be sure to include the bug number when you <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> your result</strong>
